thinkal muthal velli vare ( english : monday to friday ) is a 2015 indian malayalam comedy film , produced by anto joseph and directed by kannan thamarakkulam .   the film stars jayaram , rimi tomy , anoop menon in the lead roles along with a supporting cast of sasi kalinga , maniyanpilla raju , rachana narayanankutty , edavela babu , k. p. a. c. lalitha , and k. b. ganesh kumar .